Aadhaar Auth-xml
----------------

* Source code for generating Aadhaar-AuthXML as per 1.5 specification of Aadhaar.
* Using source code, can generate Demographic and Biometric information 

Dependencies Libraries:
----------------------
	* openssl
	* xmlsec1 (if digital signature need to be generated)

API calls in aadhaar.c
----------------------
   + PID Xml generation
 	* pidxml_biometric
	* pidxml_demographic

   + Authxml generation
   	* Authxml_biometric
   	* Authxml_demographic

   + Digital Signature
	* do_digital_signature 
	
The above calls returns appropriate xml data.

XML Security:
------------
 * v1.2.9 used
